content:
Dead tree
Released7 January 2016 (Update)
MembersYes
QuestNo
LocationHosidius
OptionsChop down
ExamineIt's only useful for firewood now.
Advanced data
Object ID1290

Sandy dead trees are a variant of dead trees that be chopped down to provide logs and 25 Woodcutting experience. They are the same as normal trees but with a different appearance. The sandy variant is located on the coast in the south-east of Hosidius.

When chopped down, the tree is replaced by a tree stump. After a few seconds, it will respawn into a dead tree.

Sandy '''dead trees''' are a variant of [[dead trees]] that be chopped down to provide [[logs]] and 25 [[Woodcutting]] experience. They are the same as normal [[tree]]s but with a different appearance. The sandy variant is located on the coast in the south-east of [[Hosidius]].

When chopped down, the tree is replaced by a [[Tree stump (dead, sandy)|tree stump]]. After a few seconds, it will respawn into a dead tree.
